# NextRole AI Configuration Template
# Copy this file to .env and add your actual API keys

# Required: Google Gemini API Key for AI Analysis
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Optional: Enhanced Features API Keys
# Get these from respective services for full functionality

# News API - for company news and updates
# Get free key at: https://newsapi.org/
